Qaf waalqur-ani almajeedi
Bal ‘ajiboo an jaahum munthirun minhum faqala alkafiroona hatha shay-on ‘ajeebun
A-itha mitna wakunna turaban thalika raj’un ba’eedun
Qad ‘alimna ma tanqusu al-ardu minhum wa’indana kitabun hafeethun
Bal kaththaboo bialhaqqi lamma jaahum fahum fee amrin mareejin
Afalam yanthuroo ila alssama-i fawqahum kayfa banaynaha wazayyannaha wama laha min furoojin
Waal-arda madadnaha waalqayna feeha rawasiya waanbatna feeha min kulli zawjin baheejin
Tabsiratan wathikra likulli ‘abdin muneebin
Wanazzalna mina alssama-i maan mubarakan faanbatna bihi jannatin wahabba alhaseedi
Waalnnakhla basiqatin laha tal’un nadeedun
Rizqan lil’ibadi waahyayna bihi baldatan maytan kathalika alkhurooju
Kaththabat qablahum qawmu noohin waas-habu alrrassi wathamoodu
Wa’adun wafir’awnu wa-ikhwanu lootin
Waas-habu al-aykati waqawmu tubba’in kullun kaththaba alrrusula fahaqqa wa’eedi
Afa’ayeena bialkhalqi al-awwali bal hum fee labsin min khalqin jadeedin
Walaqad khalaqna al-insana wana’lamu ma tuwaswisu bihi nafsuhu wanahnu aqrabu ilayhi min habli alwareedi
Ith yatalaqqa almutalaqqiyani ‘ani alyameeni wa’ani alshshimali qa’eedun
Ma yalfithu min qawlin illa ladayhi raqeebun ‘ateedun
Wajaat sakratu almawti bialhaqqi thalika ma kunta minhu taheedu
Wanufikha fee alssoori thalika yawmu alwa’eedi
Wajaat kullu nafsin ma’aha sa-iqun washaheedun
Laqad kunta fee ghaflatin min hatha fakashafna ‘anka ghitaaka fabasaruka alyawma hadeedun
Waqala qareenuhu hatha ma ladayya ‘ateedun
Alqiya fee jahannama kulla kaffarin ‘aneedin
Manna’in lilkhayri mu’tadin mureebin
Allathee ja’ala ma’a Allahi ilahan akhara faalqiyahu fee al’athabi alshshadeedi
Qala qareenuhu rabbana ma atghaytuhu walakin kana fee dalalin ba’eedin
Qala la takhtasimoo ladayya waqad qaddamtu ilaykum bialwa’eedi
Ma yubaddalu alqawlu ladayya wama ana bithallamin lil’abeedi
Yawma naqoolu lijahannama hali imtala/ti wataqoolu hal min mazeedin
Waozlifati aljannatu lilmuttaqeena ghayra ba’eedin
Hatha ma too’adoona likulli awwabin hafeethin
Man khashiya alrrahmana bialghaybi wajaa biqalbin muneebin
Odkhulooha bisalamin thalika yawmu alkhuloodi
Lahum ma yashaoona feeha waladayna mazeedun
Wakam ahlakna qablahum min qarnin hum ashaddu minhum batshan fanaqqaboo fee albiladi hal min maheesin
Inna fee thalika lathikra liman kana lahu qalbun aw alqa alssam’a wahuwa shaheedun
Walaqad khalaqna alssamawati waal-arda wama baynahuma fee sittati ayyamin wama massana min lughoobin
Faisbir ‘ala ma yaqooloona wasabbih bihamdi rabbika qabla tuloo’i alshshamsi waqabla alghuroobi
Wamina allayli fasabbihhu waadbara alssujoodi
Waistami’ yawma yunadi almunadi min makanin qareebin
Yawma yasma’oona alssayhata bialhaqqi thalika yawmu alkhurooji
Inna nahnu nuhyee wanumeetu wa-ilayna almaseeru
Yawma tashaqqaqu al-ardu ‘anhum sira’an thalika hashrun ‘alayna yaseerun
Nahnu a’lamu bima yaqooloona wama anta ‘alayhim bijabbarin fathakkir bialqurani man yakhafu wa’eedi